feat(admin): HIG redesign — glass sidebar, segmented tabs, token migration

Phase A summary (Steps 1-7):
- Step 1: Compat bridge — 17 legacy --color-* aliases trong _colors.css
  → 145 admin call-sites tự dùng theme system mới (no rewrite needed)
- Step 2: Sidebar HIG glass
  - backdrop-filter blur(24px) saturate(180%) với @supports
  - Active state: accent-soft + gradient bar accent->math
  - AI item gradient từ tokens
  - Spring drawer mobile cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.3, 0.64, 1) 360ms
  - Overlay opacity fade 240ms thay display toggle
  - Topbar + bottom nav: surface-glass token (auto-Twilight)
- Step 3: Tab bar -> Apple Segmented Control
  - Pill track surface-2 + lifted card active state
  - AI tab gradient accent->math với glow shadow
- Step 4: Badges/buttons tokenize
  - 6 type badges: subject color tints (math/geo/bio/etc)
  - .q-num, .q-correct, .role-* -> semantic tokens
  - .btn-danger/success/info -> error/success/info tokens
  - Bỏ ~12 dòng [data-theme=dark] redundancy
- Step 5: Forms/Modals
  - Focus ring -> accent + accent-soft
  - Modal overlay -> color-mix(--bg) + backdrop-filter blur(8px) saturate(140%)
  - section-card.drag-over -> accent
- Step 6: Help section + Toast + Image overlay
  - h-note/h-tip -> warning-soft/success-soft
  - .h-step-num -> accent
  - Toast borders -> semantic tokens
  - Img delete btn -> error token
- Step 7: Verified visual capture light + dark Twilight

Remaining hardcoded colors: 37 occurrences in submission-card, grade-badge, AI template specifics.
Will tokenize incrementally in Phase B.
